WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.868
Come

00:00:03.937 --> 00:00:07.338
True

00:00:12.379 --> 00:00:15.473
Penelope, dear,
so good of you to come.

00:00:15.549 --> 00:00:18.916
Thanks so much, Mrs. Potter.
Oh, isn't it lovely.

00:00:18.986 --> 00:00:21.216
You're a lucky boy, Harvey.
Yes.

00:00:21.288 --> 00:00:24.257
I know the party is going to
be a great success. I hope so.

00:00:24.324 --> 00:00:26.656
Hello, Penelope.
Oh, hello.

00:00:26.727 --> 00:00:30.026
I didn't know you were going to
be here. Anywhere that you are.
